{"tid":723943,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"依到班所謂球迷 討論場波係爭住出post笑d球員","createTime":"2018-06-30T16:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T17:10:25.000Z","uid":1779,"like":35,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5b16c451796ca5d25c54048ebb4bc8bd3a88aed6","tid":723943,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"係覺得自己好撚風趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4年1次 一世人幾可踢到2 3次世界盃<br />\n莫講世界盃 歐聯歐霸打吡 基本上所有大戰 <br />\n所謂討論 個個都準備出post又笑又講埋d九唔撚八既野<br />\n<br />\n波台班傻閪帶起風頭 跟埋班中學雞人講佢又講 <br />\n乜撚登機、訓咗無睇(係高登講足咁多年仲未厭...)、小花、牙朗 聽到依d terms真係好撚反感 <br />\n十個有九個post都一撚樣....<br />\n<br />\n聽茶記阿叔一路睇波一路9up，都好撚過依度<br />\n討論？真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"c5d078822c7122a43b2218acb69ec87f264b1be5","tid":723943,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea5e804fb8e7162b4d033ad1b057c031843243a","tid":723943,"uid":141772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"你唔係以為連登係討論區呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b254490c771b7c4cfe4ad55e80412dc130682b","tid":723943,"uid":175402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:56:23.000Z","msg":"上連登駛鬼同佢地認真咩<br />\n班傻仔覺得笑9 D球星就係識波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c33b673549937b84a49f76f930c9a9def4905ce","tid":723943,"uid":30837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:56:54.000Z","msg":"波台係高登果陣已經係咁嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e9a4ffe0cbbecf1e9badcd3045bb9d78b03a13","tid":723943,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:58:08.000Z","msg":"佢地鐘意點講就點講喇,淨係識踩同屌，都唔會欣賞下人地努力，算9數喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcab2c0138a69b37387a1da0fb5983fc